	SUBROUTINE  SHFC_2(X,Y,LSD2,NSAM,NROW,SX,SY)
d20 2
a21 2
C  Shift 2-D in Fourier space with copy; no-power-of-two dimensions
C  If SX and SY equal zero then no shift
